## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a98c6-103">這個類別的屬性值只能在 machine.config 檔案中設定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a98c6-103">Property values of this class can only be set in the machine.config file.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="a98c6-104">交易應用程式所使用的範例設定檔，如下所示，可以是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a98c6-104">An example configuration file used by your transaction application can be as follows,</span></span>  
  
 `<configuration>`  
  
 `<system.transactions>`  
  
 `<defaultSettings distributedTransactionManagerName="F04M25" timeout="02:00:00"/>`  
  
 `<machineSettings maxTimeout="02:00:00"/>`  
  
 `</system.transactions>`  
  
 `</configuration>`  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a98c6-105">這個範例會指定交易的預設值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a98c6-105">This example specifies the default values of a transaction.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a98c6-106">具體來說，它會設定電腦名稱的分散式交易協調器 (MSDTC) 負責協調所有本機，啟動的分散式的交易和在這之後交易會逾時的預設時間。此外，它會指定交易逾時前，允許在電腦層級，這是最大時間量可以只修改的設定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a98c6-106">Specifically, it sets the computer name of the Distributed Transaction Coordinator (MSDTC) that is responsible for coordinating all distributed transactions started locally, and the default time after which a transaction times out. In addition, it specifies a setting that can only be modified at the machine level, which is the maximum amount of time allowed before a transaction times out.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
